{
  "id": 5159559872249856,
  "name": "js-profiling in dedicated workers",
  "summary": "Allows js-profiling in dedicated workers\n\nThis feature enables the JavaScript Self‑Profiling (js-profiling) API in Dedicated Workers, while remaining gated by Document Policy. It allows developers to obtain low‑overhead CPU attribution for JavaScript execution in workers, with Document Policy support for workers tracked separately.",
